content: Dumb doesn't let you do anything

It is confusing to navigate. The "categories" are un labeled. The position variety see is very limited and there is absolutely no description on how to perform beyond the image. As this app is a purchase, I expected a higher quality of content and organization. The actual function of the app is smooth, but unusual to navigate. It uses a vertical transition instead of a horizontal.
This app only shows the pictures I cannot find any description of how to use those positions but use them in my version then or our version
Awesome app if you want to diverce and if looking for something different
